CMC Motors, the sole distributor of the ford ranger vehicles, and NIC Bank, have signed a partnership that will see CMC? Ford customers receive up to 95% financing on all ford ranger vehicles. This is payable within 60 months. This promotion scheme will ease the acquisition of ford ranger vehicles as customers will be able to enjoy the maximum loan tenure of 60 months. They will also enjoy 60 days repayment holiday after vehicle release and insurance services arranged through NIC Bank.